headline: This Magnificent 4.9%-Yielding Dividend Stock Continues to Cash in on This Smart Strategy
summary: It has delivered an impressive 9% compound annual dividend growth rate during that period.  Fueling the company's dividend has been its ability to grow its business through organic investment and accretive acquisitions.  One crucial factor supporting its ability to continue investing in growing its business is its smart capital recycling strategy.
